name: DanDino - Flower
description:
These handcrafted baby shoes are very soft and comfortable for those delicate feet. Made of the high-quality soft lamb leather that baby’s feet can breathe, these shoes not only protect, but also flex child’s feet.

While walking, our shoes still allow children to feel the ground, and grip with their toes. This is very important for developing strong and healthy baby’s feet. Pediatricians worldwide recommend for your baby the use of soft soled leather shoes…shoes like ours.

Gently-elasticized ankle provides easy slip on/off, so our shoes are very practical for everyday use. You can wash them in cold water with mild detergent.
